                        {
                            "defaultConfiguration": {
                                "level": "error"
                            },
                            "fullDescription": {
                                "text": "unicode loads unicode data downloaded from unicode.org into nodejs.\n\nUnicode downloads binary resources over HTTP, which leaves it vulnerable to MITM attacks."
                            },
                            "help": {
                                "markdown": "**Vulnerability NSWG-ECO-161**\n| Severity | Package | Fixed Version | Link |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n|HIGH|unicode|<0.0.0|[NSWG-ECO-161]()|\n\nunicode loads unicode data downloaded from unicode.org into nodejs.\n\nUnicode downloads binary resources over HTTP, which leaves it vulnerable to MITM attacks.",
                                "text": "Vulnerability NSWG-ECO-161\nSeverity: HIGH\nPackage: unicode\nFixed Version: <0.0.0\nLink: [NSWG-ECO-161]()\nunicode loads unicode data downloaded from unicode.org into nodejs.\n\nUnicode downloads binary resources over HTTP, which leaves it vulnerable to MITM attacks."
                            },
                            "id": "NSWG-ECO-161",
